{"tid":2182360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「捍衞民主毋須他人同意」捷克議長歷史性訪台","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T09:05:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e96702b709ab5e38763c8b23485c020ed8ebfb","tid":2182360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200831/H5FSTVW7QJGMDFO3GIMJXXPUZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200831%2FH5FSTVW7QJGMDFO3GIMJXXPUZU%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr09Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=1e2b9e11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200831%2FH5FSTVW7QJGMDFO3GIMJXXPUZU%2F&h=9d62dd04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200831/H5FSTVW7QJGMDFO3GIMJXXPUZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「捍衞民主毋須他人同意」捷克議長歷史性訪台<br />\n<br />\n捷克參議院議長維特齊（Milos Vystrcil）應立法院長游錫堃邀請，昨率領包括布拉格市長賀瑞普在內的近90人訪問團抵達台灣進行六天訪問，成為歷來到訪台灣的最高級捷克官員。維特齊明天到台灣立法院演講，3日會見台灣總統蔡英文，他出發前明言「不管他人同意與否」，強調此行是延續前總統哈維爾等建立的外交傳統，也就是捍衞自由和民主，與民主國家合作。蔡英文期望持續深化和捷克的合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hye4VNt4P1-0AiJKvDfLfEyCHsY=/960x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SBTTSFRGB5HNNLPOS6SFIG4WPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHye4VNt4P1-0AiJKvDfLfEyCHsY%3D%2F960x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSBTTSFRGB5HNNLPOS6SFIG4WPE.jpg&h=98eded26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■捷克參議院議長維特齊（左）率團訪台，台外長吳釗燮迎接。<br />\n<br />\n根據捷克憲法，參院議長在捷克憲政體制的地位僅次於總統，故是歷來到訪台灣最高級的捷克官員，外界亦形容是台灣近年最具影響力的外交突破之一。維特齊與訪團成員抵。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n團隊下機後，昨全日待在酒店，配合防疫採檢。今次台灣之旅，維特齊幾乎見盡台。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台外交大突破 將晤蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n總統蔡英文在facebook上表示，捷克和台灣一樣，在1980年代經歷民主轉型，台捷間有太。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4tlMIxluKnsFY_JaJ6GNdksQaUg=/800x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2M62TQCLNGXNJTKSVRCQODG5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4tlMIxluKnsFY_JaJ6GNdksQaUg%3D%2F800x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2M62TQCLNGXNJTKSVRCQODG5A.jpg&h=9aa9d879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■捷克代表團戴有象徵台灣捷克友誼的徽章。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cjU1t75cKrlaj3zrqANOFYb1Jx8=/567x529/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7EASL5DOSJBU7MLO4OLTJQIACQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcjU1t75cKrlaj3zrqANOFYb1Jx8%3D%2F567x529%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7EASL5DOSJBU7MLO4OLTJQIACQ.gif&h=b8d098b1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}